	   <tr><td colspan=2>ok just so you understand barbs have 3 more wisdom than a ogre thats right 3 lousy points they have 30 more strength and nearly 30 more stam.<br><br>So maybe the slightly weak choice of barb is why you do not mele or tank any.<br><br>Barbs make a ok shaman choice however might not be the best all have upside and downside<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
