	   <tr><td colspan=2>As to the mana regen it varys. Depending on your total mana and your lvl. Both make a difference. And like was said must put a point into meditation.&nbsp;&nbsp;You must use the spell hot key to meditate untill you reach lvl 35. That is when you lose your spell book. Then all you must do to meditate is sit.  If you are not using the spell book to med under lvl 35 this would be your problem.<br><br>As for why you are not getting good exp in kunark.  If you are the lowest lvl in group you will get the least amount of exp from kills. Or if you have someone more than 3 lvls higher than you at lvl 14 then you will see little exp due to that also.   It is best to keep your group within 3 lvls from highest to lowest lvl. ie: lvls 14 will group with anywehre from lvl 11 to lvl 17 but not a lvl 11 with a lvl 17. That is a 6 lvl difference and the lvl 11 will get no exp. Or too little to measure.<br><br>Hope this helps you both.  =)<br>&nbsp;<br>Kuzain<br>49 Shaman</td></tr>
